# PRD Instructions (Product Requirements Document)

## Purpose
Briefly explain the purpose and expected business/user outcomes.

## Problem Statement
Describe the problem to be solved or opportunity to address.

## Acceptance Criteria
- List clear, testable conditions for success.

## Background/Context
Describe the context, user needs, regulatory requirements, etc.

## Dependencies
- List blocking issues, dependencies, or other teams.

## Stakeholders
- List involved parties, reviewers, approvers.
